{"tid":1250353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支那4閨蜜唱歌搶付錢　竟鬧到1女跳公園池塘斃命","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T03:23:15.000Z","uid":122,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"117550f357b8e1fe6f7a21cbba5fe3c2fc30073f","tid":1250353,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"搶付錢竟然搶出人命！中國浙江省4名閨蜜在2018年4月時一起相約吃火鍋，飯後又續攤去唱KTV，結果其中一人李筱筱搶著埋單被阻止，氣憤動手打了閨蜜陳靜兩耳光，結果引發在場大亂鬥，後來靠著許逸飛割腕濺血震驚眾人才平息紛爭。想不到事後李筱筱情緒難平，竟然跑到公園池塘投水自殺身亡，李女家屬向在場眾人提告求償50萬元人民幣（約231萬元台幣），近日以15萬元人民幣（約69萬元台幣）達成和解。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《浙江日報》報導，李筱筱、陳靜在高中就是好友，後來又結識了張欣雨、許逸飛兩人，4女都是20多歲，經常一起聚會。去年10月時4女相約吃火鍋，席間氣氛融洽，之後又到KTV續攤，許逸飛還找了3名男性友人一起來唱歌，直接凌晨1時多要散場回家時卻發生了衝突。<br />\n<br />\n當晚眾人在KTV消費了1300元人民幣（約5994元台幣），李筱筱搶著付錢，陳靜和張欣雨知道她經濟情況並沒有很好，並阻止她埋單，結果讓李筱筱動怒，直接甩了陳靜兩耳光，張欣雨為維護陳靜，將李筱筱推倒在地，之後便引發眾人衝突。<br />\n<br />\n本來酒醉躺在沙發上睡覺的許逸飛被爭執聲吵醒，勸阻無效，便以割腕來要脅，大家見她手腕濺血，瞬間停止了爭執，急忙將許逸飛送醫治療，所幸許逸飛沒有生命危險。然而等到眾人剛放鬆下來時，突然發現李筱筱不見了，隨即又開始焦急尋找，結果陳靜在一處公園池塘旁看見蹲在地上的李女，李女一看陳靜接近，便投水自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n公安機關調查認定李筱筱是自殺，但李女父母認為當晚女兒是與其他人發生爭執，產生負面情緒才會尋短，認為在場人士應至少負擔一半的責任，故要求女兒的3名閨蜜和同樣在場的3名男子，合計賠償50萬元人民幣。寧波鎮海法院近日調解，最後6人賠償15萬元人民幣和李女父母達成和解。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/7-21-2015/_OLuhE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F7-21-2015%2F_OLuhE.gif&h=4fa33411&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3e01f83e500154508fc208cff36db845ab82503","tid":1250353,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"冇得屌<br />\n嘥晒"},{"pid":"8d447750acbd23c44e3f6e380742c33a780935af","tid":1250353,"uid":264965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"這就是  中國"},{"pid":"77d61746dc41c45d1f7bc03812dfdca31879ea8f","tid":1250353,"uid":196087,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"好撚on9"},{"pid":"789820b42c93d4fb6823111d3e39bdbb0aed18a8","tid":1250353,"uid":38777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:03:19.000Z","msg":"中國入面真係乜嘢都可以發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde831efad42c17a1dcca9be0b51a58516dcd7f","tid":1250353,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d43e29d9481767a62867f5940f140d13735a32","tid":1250353,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"請客"},{"pid":"4993537359825fcd995501823ef2ade6d5baa1e0","tid":1250353,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2249cc21243bbdf9f3d107bd47523699a8539e","tid":1250353,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d6fcb96cf55f12b3686795d42c065970f15333","tid":1250353,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"啱啦 呢啲廢物死多啲"},{"pid":"2db63431e86e2a064dcca097b6a1d80e8494a079","tid":1250353,"uid":34757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46d639e2eb0d69b0ba41f712673f1869efdc0495","tid":1250353,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"瘋了"},{"pid":"47692caf6120f2b3701385f67e88426afacf0157","tid":1250353,"uid":24449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"中國人是最喜歡請客的一個民族。從搶付車費，搶會鈔，以至於大宴客，沒有一件事不足以表示中國是一個禮讓之邦。我的錢就是你的錢，你的錢也就是我的錢，大家不分彼此；你可以吃我的，用我的，因為咱們是一家人。這種情形，西洋人覺得很奇怪。恕我淺陋，我沒有見過西洋人搶付過車費，或搶會過鈔。我們在歐洲做學生的時代，因為窮，大家也主張「西化」，飯館裏吃飯，各自付各自的錢，相約不搶 會鈔。西洋人宴客是有的，但是極不輕易有一次，最普通的只是來一個茶會，並不像中國人這樣常常請朋友吃飯。這些事情，都顯得中國人比西洋人更慷慨更會應酬。<br />\n<br />\n其實，中國人這種應酬是利用人們喜歡佔便宜的心理。不花錢可以白坐車，白吃飯，白看戲，等等，受惠的人應該是高興的。一高興，再高興，三高興，高興的次數越多，被請的人對於請客的人就越有好印象。如果被請的人比我的地位高，他可以「有求必應」助我升官發財；如果被請的人比我的地位底，他也可以到處吹噓，逢人說項，增加我的聲譽，間接地於我有益。中國人向來主張「受人錢財，與人消災」的，不花錢而可以白坐車，白吃飯，白看戲，也就等於受人錢財，若不與人消災，就該為人造福。由此看來，請客乃是一種「小往大來」的政策，請客的錢不是白花的。"},{"pid":"1c0f71177420660c137e390653d2906f0ac53f38","tid":1250353,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"扮搶咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122c95128dfe1671535755acad311147ad2a22e2","tid":1250353,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0939549ecd3380bac8d3775eabb5ecd1814d2161","tid":1250353,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐～"},{"pid":"75b54398aadca96ae706f175269334ef667e068a","tid":1250353,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:44:31.000Z","msg":"睇到割脈嗰到笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a925cfa121f0def4ffa82e5185b29c8d519b890","tid":1250353,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75b54398aadca96ae706f175269334ef667e068a","tid":1250353,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:44:31.000Z","msg":"睇到割脈嗰到笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"誇張到假假地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}